OL,3,CMan jailed for subjecting woman to
OL,4,Cprolonged campaign of controlling
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for three years
OL,8,Ffor subjecting a woman to a prolonged
OL,9,Fcampaign of controlling and abusive
OL,10,Fbehaviour in Crawley.
OL,12,FLee Yates controlled many aspects of
OL,13,Fthe woman, in her 40s, life, including
OL,14,Fwhat clothes she wore and how long she
OL,15,Fcould bathe for.
OL,17,FHe also would not allow her to fall
OL,18,Fasleep before him or stay in bed
OL,19,Flonger than him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
