PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776845134
OL,3,CMan jailed for subjecting woman to
OL,4,Cprolonged campaign of controlling
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FThe woman was forced to make his meals
OL,8,Fand give him any of her spare money.
OL,9,FArguments were met with physical abuse
OL,10,Fand threats to kill her pets.
OL,12,FYates was also accused of raping the
OL,13,Fwoman on two occasions.
OL,15,FThe incidents were reported to police
OL,16,Fand Yates was arrested while the
OL,17,Fvictim was safeguarded and supported
OL,18,Fby specialist officers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
