OL,3,CMan jailed for subjecting woman to
OL,4,Cprolonged campaign of controlling
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHe was subsequently charged with
OL,13,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour,
OL,14,Fand two counts of rape.
OL,16,FAt Lewes Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,17,FApril 2, he was found guilty of
OL,18,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour,
OL,19,Fand not guilty of both counts of rape.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
