CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776845134
OL,3,CMan jailed for subjecting woman to
OL,4,Cprolonged campaign of controlling
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FInvestigator Hannah Lane said: "Lee
OL,8,FYates sought to control almost every
OL,9,Faspect of this victim's life, using
OL,10,Fviolence and intimidation to try and
OL,11,Fsubdue her.
OL,13,F"But he underestimated her strength.
OL,14,FThanks to her reporting his crimes to
OL,15,Fthe police, he is now safely behind
OL,16,Fbars while she can look to rebuild her
OL,17,Flife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
