CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776845134
OL,3,CMan jailed for subjecting woman to
OL,4,Cprolonged campaign of controlling
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"Our message to any victims of
OL,8,Fcoercive or controlling behaviour is
OL,9,Fthat you are not alone and help is out
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,F"Report it to the police, a friend, or
OL,13,Fany other source of support, and we
OL,14,Fwill do all we can to protect you."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
